Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.96,0:00:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字叫本須和秀樹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.60,0:00:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今年生日過後就滿19歲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.97,0:00:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在是18歲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.00,0:00:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今年春天預定到東京唸大學
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.38,0:00:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.52,0:01:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，正式成為大學生…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.83,0:01:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本來應該是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.90,0:01:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,落榜了！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.50,0:01:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒考上！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.93,0:01:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得重考了！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.87,0:01:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此，我就去補習班
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.21,0:01:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到補習班努力用功
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.71,0:01:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明年我一定考上給你看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.84,0:01:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了，既然要去就去東京吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.71,0:01:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正想唸的學校也在東京
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.88,0:01:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.95,0:01:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，我要去東京！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.88,0:03:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，甦醒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.02,0:03:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終於到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.76,0:03:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是東京
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.13,0:03:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不論到哪裡都好多人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.00,0:03:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看看，公寓是在…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.84,0:03:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距離目的地約45分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.27,0:03:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在池袋換車，然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.74,0:03:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是電腦耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.58,0:03:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次親眼看到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.62,0:03:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近這個時代\NIT 科技與網際網路之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.02,0:04:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變得相當發達
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.79,0:04:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生活似乎變得非常便利
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.66,0:04:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其中最厲害的就是這種電腦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.73,0:04:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做得像真人一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.06,0:04:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不太懂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.07,0:04:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但聽說它有很多不同的功能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.27,0:04:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我家住的鄉下地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.61,0:04:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本就沒人有電腦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.34,0:04:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒喔，好棒喔，電腦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.91,0:04:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好想要喔，好想要喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.58,0:04:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種價錢我怎麼可能買得起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.85,0:04:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在表演嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.72,0:04:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個人是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.59,0:04:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為春天到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.35,0:04:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.32,0:04:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以看他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.67,0:04:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的好丟臉喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.17,0:04:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得把自言自語的習慣改掉才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.94,0:04:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟至今為止\N我身邊盡是些牛啊馬的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.75,0:05:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過電腦真的好像人類
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.92,0:05:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且又那麼的可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.46,0:05:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但也未免太貴了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.29,0:05:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,世人對這件事都沒意見嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.70,0:05:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道說都市人都很有錢嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.40,0:05:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以貧窮的重考生不准買？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.93,0:05:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.60,0:05:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.17,0:05:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也好想買台電腦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.17,0:05:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好想收發郵件
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.34,0:05:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好想看網路的色情網站
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.78,0:05:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,色情？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.81,0:05:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是…那個…這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.22,0:05:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這樣的美女面前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.15,0:05:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我竟然如此失態
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.45,0:05:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，對了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.02,0:05:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我正在找一棟公寓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.16,0:05:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問妳有聽過嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.23,0:05:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它的名字很奇怪\N叫作“ GAB 城崎”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.90,0:05:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.80,0:05:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就是“ GAB 城崎”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.57,0:05:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，就是這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.24,0:06:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您就是本須和秀樹先生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.41,0:06:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.68,0:06:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是這裡的管理員\N日比谷千歲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.62,0:06:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.69,0:06:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.19,0:06:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自來水跟瓦斯馬上都能用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.06,0:06:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總開關在這上面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.09,0:06:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好窄喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.20,0:06:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過也是沒辦法的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.76,0:06:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,租金一個月才兩萬…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.73,0:06:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,送達的行李\N已經先幫您搬進房間了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.04,0:06:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道這樣可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.30,0:06:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的，謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.47,0:06:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過應該很重吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.81,0:06:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,箱子這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.41,0:06:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.45,0:06:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.68,0:06:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為幫您搬進來的是新保先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.68,0:06:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.28,0:06:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他差不多也回來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.72,0:06:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他住在隔壁的204號房
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.49,0:06:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.69,0:06:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待會兒得謝謝他才行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.46,0:06:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，以後請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.33,0:06:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才要請妳多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.73,0:06:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.93,0:06:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.24,0:07:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是個超漂亮的管理員
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.61,0:07:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她說她住在101號房
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.31,0:07:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能住進這麼漂亮的人住的公寓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.68,0:07:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好我真的很走運
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.28,0:07:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.68,0:07:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道是管理員小姐嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.42,0:07:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.76,0:07:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你，恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.96,0:07:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你搬家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.20,0:07:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是啥玩意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.30,0:07:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master ，這個人好可怕喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.54,0:07:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.44,0:07:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嚇到你了是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.44,0:07:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請…請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.51,0:07:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.61,0:07:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫新保弘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.35,0:07:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是住在隔壁204號房的房客
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.82,0:07:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你幫我搬行李的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.58,0:07:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.49,0:07:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.75,0:07:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.22,0:07:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫我新保就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.66,0:07:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別用敬語啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.12,0:07:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你幾歲？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.76,0:07:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,18
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.63,0:08:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我一樣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.73,0:08:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,18？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.73,0:08:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後你下禮拜就要去唸\N“關補習班”對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.87,0:08:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.94,0:08:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,落榜二人組
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.67,0:08:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.50,0:08:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的，真的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.51,0:08:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.61,0:08:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那，這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.04,0:08:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的電腦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.41,0:08:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好小喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.68,0:08:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為是攜帶式的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.65,0:08:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.72,0:08:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.75,0:08:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫絲茉茉，請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.16,0:08:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒喔，好棒喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.26,0:08:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.03,0:08:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦\N你的反應太誇張了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.26,0:08:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有攜帶式電腦嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.86,0:08:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該說是，我連電腦都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.70,0:08:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這種時代，你的確很罕見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.80,0:08:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且就算買了我也不會用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.04,0:08:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這東西只要打開開關就會動的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.48,0:08:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的事， OS 會自己幫你做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.88,0:08:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你懂得還真多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.98,0:08:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很熟這東西是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.95,0:08:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,普通啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.08,0:08:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電腦真的很棒嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.78,0:08:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那當然
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.82,0:08:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以用絲茉茉打電話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.79,0:08:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也可以收郵件
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.69,0:09:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以上網嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.86,0:09:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.59,0:09:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然也可以上色情網站
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.79,0:09:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎，也可以上色情網站啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.39,0:09:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,色情網站算是基本的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.63,0:09:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,色情網站，色情網…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.13,0:09:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,需要加熱嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.60,0:09:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.00,0:09:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.44,0:09:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,熱好了之後我會通知您
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.71,0:09:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請您稍坐片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.94,0:09:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.18,0:09:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.62,0:09:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來\N電腦真的好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.58,0:09:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連收銀機都會用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.69,0:09:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保那台好像是叫作絲茉茉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.39,0:09:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來也有那麼小台的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.69,0:09:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他說也能用來打電話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.09,0:09:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.83,0:09:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要歸想要\N不過實在太貴了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.54,0:09:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,況且我到現在\N連電腦的“電”字都不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.11,0:09:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底要拿來做些什麼\N我完全不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.77,0:09:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,色情網站我是會去看啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.15,0:09:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好喔，電腦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.75,0:10:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然都已經做成人型  的了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.62,0:10:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那種長得非常可愛的\N不知道有沒有掉在路上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.39,0:10:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是不可能的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.33,0:10:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，有人死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.70,0:10:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是殺人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.47,0:10:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是殺人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.31,0:10:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這算是殺人事件嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.01,0:10:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.84,0:10:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛搬到東京第一天\N就被捲進了殺人事件嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.58,0:10:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.51,0:10:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遇到這種情況該怎麼做？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.85,0:10:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該先做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.85,0:10:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫警察？還是叫救護車？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.68,0:10:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想想…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.85,0:10:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那對耳朵…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.39,0:10:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那好像跟我今天\N在車站前電器行看到的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.79,0:10:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼，別嚇我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.09,0:10:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害我以為是什麼\N懸疑殺人事件呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.97,0:10:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.64,0:10:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是快點回去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.74,0:10:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把房間整理整理好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.97,0:11:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.74,0:11:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是電腦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.94,0:11:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後這裡是垃圾場
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.11,0:11:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說，這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.58,0:11:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是垃圾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.22,0:11:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.28,0:11:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我拿走這個也無所謂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.05,0:11:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以吧？可以吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.79,0:11:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.15,0:11:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來，產業廢棄物這些東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.39,0:11:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是越少越好才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.06,0:11:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為會產生戴奧辛之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.06,0:11:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二氧化碳也會破壞臭氧層
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.16,0:11:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.51,0:11:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…這就是電腦的重量嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.72,0:11:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重的要死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.03,0:12:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來電腦這麼重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.07,0:12:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.93,0:12:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家說開機很重或很輕鬆\N（日文“開機很重”意指“很慢”）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.77,0:12:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.17,0:12:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽新保說他那台很輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.71,0:12:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來攜帶式真的很輕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.15,0:12:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過看她這個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.45,0:12:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟人類女孩沒什麼兩樣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.62,0:12:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.76,0:12:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又柔軟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.36,0:12:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這應該還很新吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.67,0:12:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是因為買了新機種\N所以才被丟掉的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.74,0:12:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.54,0:12:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會好好地物盡其用的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.84,0:12:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，快來用看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.11,0:12:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想想，該怎麼做呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.45,0:12:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我記得新保說過\N只要按 下開關就會動了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.98,0:12:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開關，開關，開關，開關，開關
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.92,0:12:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.85,0:12:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.52,0:12:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開關在哪裡啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.69,0:13:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒有地方可以按了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.13,0:13:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡也按了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.06,0:13:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡也按了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.03,0:13:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡也按了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.96,0:13:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡也按了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.60,0:13:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡也按了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.03,0:13:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我把突起的部份全按遍了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.60,0:13:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全部
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.20,0:13:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全部…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.94,0:13:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.84,0:13:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡面？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.15,0:13:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.98,0:13:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能會有這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.68,0:13:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是只差那裡沒按 過…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.86,0:13:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒有什麼下流的念頭喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.03,0:13:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不會動的話\N我會很困擾的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.67,0:13:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不會動的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.17,0:13:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.24,0:13:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.86,0:15:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.50,0:15:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.20,0:15:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.64,0:15:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.87,0:15:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是妳的名字嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.18,0:15:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.24,0:15:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.11,0:15:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.38,0:15:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.65,0:15:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這台電腦雖然勉強動了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.98,0:15:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是除了“ちぃ”之外\N什麼都不會講
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.42,0:15:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全身赤裸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.32,0:15:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後又非常的可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.29,0:15:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.29,0:15:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有，我有看過這種場景
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.06,0:15:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在路上撿到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.03,0:15:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或是突然闖進一個\N很可愛的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.00,0:15:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有著不可思議的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.63,0:15:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事都會做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.70,0:15:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚至還愛上一起同居的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.30,0:15:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事都幫忙做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.47,0:15:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不論是煮菜、打掃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.97,0:16:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或是那方面的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.21,0:16:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.48,0:16:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我果然太走運了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.45,0:16:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.05,0:16:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是新保
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.95,0:16:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要去洗澡？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.28,0:16:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我平常都去附近健康中心的澡堂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.15,0:16:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也知道吧\N因為這公寓沒有浴室嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.22,0:16:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔，我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.59,0:16:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能馬上出門嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.59,0:16:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上幫你開門
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.76,0:16:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂…全身裸體！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.89,0:16:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是理所當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.86,0:16:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為要去洗澡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.20,0:16:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.26,0:16:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道你是那種\N不穿泳褲就不敢洗的人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.60,0:16:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.23,0:16:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，沒有，沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.14,0:16:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不太妙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.04,0:16:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種狀況實在不太妙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.84,0:16:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.78,0:16:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衣服，衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.94,0:16:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有什麼衣服，可以穿的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.08,0:16:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有，沒有，沒有，沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.38,0:16:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早知道應該在箱子寫上\N裡面裝的是什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.82,0:16:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，是毛巾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.82,0:16:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過暫時先…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.49,0:16:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.02,0:16:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看…看起來更性感了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.76,0:16:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，還沒好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.29,0:16:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再找件能穿的，能穿的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.96,0:16:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.86,0:16:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.97,0:17:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.40,0:17:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你找不到要帶去澡堂的東西嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.17,0:17:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.20,0:17:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我幫忙嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.00,0:17:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.57,0:17:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用客氣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.74,0:17:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪，門沒鎖嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.58,0:17:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我忘了鎖門
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.31,0:17:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之，先把她藏起來…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.31,0:17:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.28,0:17:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.52,0:17:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇，怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.22,0:17:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,房間怎麼弄得亂七八糟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.25,0:17:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不用那麼著急
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.62,0:17:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正澡堂開到12點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.99,0:17:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.86,0:17:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你流鼻血了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.89,0:17:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊，不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.66,0:17:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是稍微跌了一跤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.30,0:17:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.43,0:17:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是要找洗髮精之類的\N應該很困難吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.10,0:17:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的借你用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.80,0:17:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.74,0:17:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毛巾呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.60,0:17:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毛巾我有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.94,0:17:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，不是，雖然有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.81,0:17:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過正在使用中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.58,0:17:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.18,0:17:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別在意，別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.34,0:17:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在自言自語
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.48,0:17:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.78,0:17:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會在房裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.02,0:17:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你準備好了，就來叫我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.85,0:17:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔，我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.82,0:17:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就過去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.15,0:17:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.36,0:18:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.70,0:18:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.13,0:18:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.36,0:18:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.43,0:18:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有，那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.63,0:18:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我又跌了一跤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.70,0:18:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.20,0:18:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.74,0:18:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有…有什麼事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.31,0:18:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你沒有換洗的衣物\N我的可以借你穿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.41,0:18:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.18,0:18:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係，沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.28,0:18:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有帶來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.68,0:18:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就過去\N你回房裡等我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.51,0:18:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好嗎？好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.85,0:18:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.26,0:18:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還有事忘了講
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.43,0:18:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.99,0:18:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別嚇我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.76,0:18:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.70,0:18:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.30,0:18:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,澡堂的費用要400円
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.10,0:18:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果要用三溫暖\N還要再加300円
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.80,0:18:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.04,0:18:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.41,0:18:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.45,0:19:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉，好累喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.89,0:19:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.36,0:19:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待在這裡不要動，知道了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.90,0:19:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.27,0:19:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保啊，你可不可以不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.70,0:19:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.70,0:19:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有…有什麼事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.77,0:19:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是牛蒡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.11,0:19:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果您不討厭的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.04,0:19:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？給我的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.71,0:19:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.55,0:19:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇，謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.22,0:19:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我煮太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.05,0:19:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不會造成您困擾的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.82,0:19:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪有什麼困擾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.52,0:19:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.46,0:19:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一點都沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.02,0:19:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.46,0:19:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次如果我還有做什麼好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.06,0:19:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我再拿來給您吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.03,0:19:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.26,0:19:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，如果您不嫌棄的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.60,0:19:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好高興
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.40,0:19:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.11,0:19:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幫了我一個大忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.61,0:19:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太感動了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.38,0:19:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.51,0:20:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.38,0:20:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀，哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.42,0:20:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.68,0:20:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是電腦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.42,0:20:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是可愛的電腦小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.49,0:20:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的，那是電腦\N所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.39,0:20:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼本須和先生，電腦小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.49,0:20:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.06,0:20:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.83,0:20:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管…管理員小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.54,0:20:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉，她一定認為我是變態
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.64,0:20:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以為我把電腦的衣服脫光\N然後一個人在暗爽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.88,0:20:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好…好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.91,0:20:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？不去澡堂了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.65,0:20:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.55,0:20:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.62,0:20:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為想在今天把房間整理好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.02,0:20:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.76,0:20:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了，那就沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.42,0:20:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.86,0:20:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.99,0:20:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用那麼在意啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.13,0:20:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.07,0:20:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.74,0:21:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.27,0:21:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在慌什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.67,0:21:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對方只是電腦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.94,0:21:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.25,0:21:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.95,0:21:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我問妳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.18,0:21:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.62,0:21:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳只會說“ちぃ”嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.65,0:21:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.73,0:21:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟是在垃圾場撿來的電腦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.73,0:21:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…該不會是哪裡壞了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.88,0:21:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別露出那種表情啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.05,0:21:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是在想說\N自己又要被丟掉了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.39,0:21:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然都把妳撿回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.06,0:21:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會好好愛惜妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.10,0:21:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.93,0:22:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，真的好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.94,0:22:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滑嫩嫩的，暖呼呼的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.94,0:22:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有這對耳朵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.28,0:22:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就像是普通的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.78,0:22:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胸部也好軟…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.71,0:23:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能撿到這麼可愛的電腦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.72,0:24:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真是超幸運啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.28,0:24:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.45,0:24:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是她只會說“ちぃ”
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.26,0:24:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是哪裡故障了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.12,0:24:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也完全不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.23,0:24:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.09,0:24:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.93,0:24:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要到新保介紹的\N那個很懂電腦的人家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.20,0:24:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許可以知道些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.63,0:24:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.50,0:24:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chobits 下一回\N「ちぃ，出門」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.91,0:24:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.57,0:24:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,網路上的都市傳說？